Bronx Net News "Gail" Character Project
Gail is a 2D animated character who airs live every Friday on the Bronx net news channel segment (OPEN). 
Her creator, Michael Ferraro, created a software program to animate Gail during segments. 
Created new movements, fixed existing animation movements, layered body parts for clothing possibility, and created background sets for animations and promotions. 
Controlled animation movements of “Gail” during live television segments.

Details:
Adobe Flash
2D Animation
2D animated character
Bronxnet news (Open) on Fridays @10:00am
Technical Puppeteering

